@startuml UC19_Sequence
title UC19: 配置系统设置 - 顺序图

actor "管理员" as Admin
boundary "配置门户" as Portal
control "系统管理控制器" as AdminCtrl
entity "SystemConfig" as Config
entity "Announcement" as Announcement

Admin -> Portal : 设置时间、主题或发布公告
Portal -> AdminCtrl : updateSettings(settings)
AdminCtrl -> Config : saveParams(params)
opt 发布公告
    AdminCtrl -> Announcement : create(content)
end
Config --> AdminCtrl : success
AdminCtrl --> Portal : 配置生效提示
@enduml
